  <body dur="03:52.690">
    <div begin="00:00.980" end="03:52.690">
      <p begin="00:00.980" end="00:04.280" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L1"><span begin="00:00.980" end="00:01.220">あ</span><span begin="00:01.220" end="00:01.430">な</span><span begin="00:01.430" end="00:01.690">た</span><span begin="00:01.690" end="00:02.000">が</span><span begin="00:02.120" end="00:02.620">空</span><span begin="00:02.620" end="00:03.090">白</span><span begin="00:03.090" end="00:03.310">を</span><span begin="00:03.310" end="00:03.510">埋</span><span begin="00:03.510" end="00:03.760">め</span><span begin="00:03.760" end="00:03.960">る</span><span begin="00:03.960" end="00:04.280">度</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">你每一次填补空白之时</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">你每一次填補空白之時</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Every time you fill in the blanks</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">당신이 공백을 채울 때마다</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Chaque fois que tu combles le vide</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Cada vez que llenas el vacío</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Jedes Mal wenn du die Leere füllst</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Toda vez que você preenche o vazio</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Каждый раз когда ты заполняешь пустоту</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ogni volta che tu riempi il vuoto</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Anata ga kuuhaku o umeru tabi</span></p>
      <p begin="00:04.340" end="00:07.240" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L2"><span begin="00:04.340" end="00:04.710">推</span><span begin="00:04.710" end="00:05.170">測</span><span begin="00:05.170" end="00:05.650">断</span><span begin="00:05.650" end="00:05.750">つ</span><span begin="00:05.750" end="00:05.990">意</span><span begin="00:05.990" end="00:06.220">味</span><span begin="00:06.220" end="00:06.370">を</span><span begin="00:06.370" end="00:06.840">教</span><span begin="00:06.840" end="00:07.080">え</span><span begin="00:07.080" end="00:07.240">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">请告诉我 斩断猜测的意义</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">請告訴我 斬斷猜測的意義</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Tell me the meaning of severing speculation</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">추측을 끊어내는 의미를 가르쳐 줘</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Apprends-moi le sens de trancher les conjectures</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Dime el significado de cortar las sospechas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Verrate mir den Sinn Vermutungen zu beenden</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Ensine-me o significado de cortar as conjecturas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Расскажи мне в чём смысл обрывать догадки</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Dimmi il significato di troncare le supposizioni</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Suisoku tatsu imi o oshiete</span></p>
      <p begin="00:08.210" end="00:11.450" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L3"><span begin="00:08.210" end="00:08.900">私</span><span begin="00:08.900" end="00:09.190">が</span><span begin="00:09.340" end="00:09.830">空</span><span begin="00:09.830" end="00:10.290">白</span><span begin="00:10.290" end="00:10.560">を</span><span begin="00:10.560" end="00:10.730">埋</span><span begin="00:10.730" end="00:10.950">め</span><span begin="00:10.950" end="00:11.160">る</span><span begin="00:11.160" end="00:11.450">度</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我每一次填补空白之时</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我每一次填補空白之時</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Every time I fill in the blanks</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">내가 공백을 채울 때마다</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Chaque fois que je comble le vide</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Cada vez que yo lleno el vacío</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Jedes Mal wenn ich die Leere fülle</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Toda vez que eu preencho o vazio</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Каждый раз когда я заполняю пустоту</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ogni volta che io riempio il vuoto</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Watashi ga kuuhaku o umeru tabi</span></p>
      <p begin="00:11.560" end="00:14.560" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L4"><span begin="00:11.560" end="00:12.030">痛</span><span begin="00:12.030" end="00:12.530">覚</span><span begin="00:12.530" end="00:12.860">立</span><span begin="00:12.860" end="00:12.970">つ</span><span begin="00:12.970" end="00:13.190">意</span><span begin="00:13.190" end="00:13.430">味</span><span begin="00:13.430" end="00:13.660">を</span><span begin="00:13.660" end="00:14.070">教</span><span begin="00:14.070" end="00:14.340">え</span><span begin="00:14.340" end="00:14.560">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">请告诉我 痛觉苏醒的意义</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">請告訴我 痛覺甦醒的意義</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Tell me the meaning of awakening pain</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">통각이 깨어나는 의미를 가르쳐 줘</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Apprends-moi le sens de l'éveil de la douleur</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Dime el significado de que el dolor despierte</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Verrate mir den Sinn dass der Schmerz erwacht</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Ensine-me o significado do sentido da dor despertar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Расскажи мне в чём смысл пробуждения боли</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Dimmi il significato del risveglio del dolore</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Tsuukaku tatsu imi o oshiete</span></p>
      <p begin="00:14.960" end="00:16.140" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L5"><span begin="00:14.960" end="00:15.230">い</span><span begin="00:15.230" end="00:15.450">い</span><span begin="00:15.450" end="00:15.640">で</span><span begin="00:15.640" end="00:15.890">す</span><span begin="00:15.890" end="00:16.090">か</span><span begin="00:16.090" end="00:16.140">？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">可以吗？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">可以嗎？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Is it alright?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">괜찮을까?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Est-ce permis ?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">¿Te parece bien?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ist es in Ordnung?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Tudo bem?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Можно ли?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Va bene?</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ii desu ka?</span></p>
      <p begin="00:29.870" end="00:33.170" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L6"><span begin="00:29.870" end="00:30.130">あ</span><span begin="00:30.130" end="00:30.340">な</span><span begin="00:30.340" end="00:30.550">た</span><span begin="00:30.550" end="00:30.770">が</span><span begin="00:30.970" end="00:31.340">空</span><span begin="00:31.340" end="00:31.940">白</span><span begin="00:31.940" end="00:32.180">を</span><span begin="00:32.180" end="00:32.380">埋</span><span begin="00:32.380" end="00:32.620">め</span><span begin="00:32.620" end="00:32.820">る</span><span begin="00:32.820" end="00:33.170">度</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">你每一次填补空白之时</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">你每一次填補空白之時</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Every time you fill in the blanks</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">당신이 공백을 채울 때마다</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Chaque fois que tu combles le vide</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Cada vez que llenas el vacío</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Jedes Mal wenn du die Leere füllst</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Toda vez que você preenche o vazio</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Каждый раз когда ты заполняешь пустоту</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ogni volta che tu riempi il vuoto</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Anata ga kuuhaku o umeru tabi</span></p>
