      <p begin="00:37.080" end="00:40.410" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L8"><span begin="00:37.080" end="00:37.800">私</span><span begin="00:37.800" end="00:38.020">が</span><span begin="00:38.190" end="00:38.610">空</span><span begin="00:38.610" end="00:39.150">白</span><span begin="00:39.150" end="00:39.430">を</span><span begin="00:39.430" end="00:39.590">埋</span><span begin="00:39.590" end="00:39.820">め</span><span begin="00:39.820" end="00:40.030">る</span><span begin="00:40.030" end="00:40.410">度</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我每一次填补空白之时</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我每一次填補空白之時</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Every time I fill in the blanks</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">내가 공백을 채울 때마다</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Chaque fois que je comble le vide</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Cada vez que yo lleno el vacío</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Jedes Mal wenn ich die Leere fülle</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Toda vez que eu preencho o vazio</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Каждый раз когда я заполняю пустоту</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ogni volta che io riempio il vuoto</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Watashi ga kuuhaku o umeru tabi</span></p>
      <p begin="00:40.480" end="00:43.380" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L9"><span begin="00:40.480" end="00:40.930">痛</span><span begin="00:40.930" end="00:41.390">覚</span><span begin="00:41.390" end="00:41.730">立</span><span begin="00:41.730" end="00:41.850">つ</span><span begin="00:41.850" end="00:42.070">意</span><span begin="00:42.070" end="00:42.310">味</span><span begin="00:42.310" end="00:42.470">を</span><span begin="00:42.470" end="00:42.980">教</span><span begin="00:42.980" end="00:43.170">え</span><span begin="00:43.170" end="00:43.380">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">请告诉我 痛觉苏醒的意义</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">請告訴我 痛覺甦醒的意義</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Tell me the meaning of awakening pain</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">통각이 깨어나는 의미를 가르쳐 줘</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Apprends-moi le sens de l'éveil de la douleur</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Dime el significado de que el dolor despierte</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Verrate mir den Sinn dass der Schmerz erwacht</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Ensine-me o significado do sentido da dor despertar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Расскажи мне в чём смысл пробуждения боли</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Dimmi il significato del risveglio del dolore</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Tsuukaku tatsu imi o oshiete</span></p>
      <p begin="00:43.830" end="00:47.610" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L10"><span begin="00:43.830" end="00:44.330">隘</span><span begin="00:44.330" end="00:44.520">路</span><span begin="00:44.520" end="00:44.790">か</span><span begin="00:44.790" end="00:44.980">ら</span><span begin="00:44.980" end="00:45.460">急</span><span begin="00:45.460" end="00:45.680">に</span><span begin="00:45.680" end="00:45.890">伸</span><span begin="00:45.890" end="00:46.250">ば</span><span begin="00:46.250" end="00:46.340">し</span><span begin="00:46.340" end="00:46.590">た</span><span begin="00:46.590" end="00:47.010">低</span><span begin="00:47.010" end="00:47.270">能</span><span begin="00:47.270" end="00:47.480">さ</span><span begin="00:47.480" end="00:47.610">が</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">从绝境中突然流露的笨拙</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">從絕境中突然流露的笨拙</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The inadequacy suddenly reaching out from the impasse</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">막다른 길에서 갑자기 뻗어 나온 서투름이</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Cette bêtise soudainement tendue depuis l'impasse</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Esa torpeza que se extendió de pronto desde el callejón</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Die Unbeholfenheit die sich jäh aus der Sackgasse streckt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">A inaptidão que subitamente se estendeu do beco sem saída</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Бездарность внезапно проявленная в тупике</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">L'inettitudine allungata all'improvviso da un vicolo cieco</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Airo kara kyuu ni nobashita teinou-sa ga</span></p>
      <p begin="00:47.890" end="00:50.770" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L11"><span begin="00:47.890" end="00:48.580">左</span><span begin="00:48.580" end="00:48.940">利</span><span begin="00:48.940" end="00:49.070">き</span><span begin="00:49.070" end="00:49.310">に</span><span begin="00:49.310" end="00:49.690">反</span><span begin="00:49.690" end="00:49.960">射</span><span begin="00:49.960" end="00:50.180">し</span><span begin="00:50.180" end="00:50.770">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">竟本能地偏向左侧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">竟本能地偏向左側</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Was reflected in my left-handedness</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">왼손잡이에 반사되었어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">S'est reflétée instinctivement sur ma main gauche</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Se reflejó en mi lado zurdo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Hat sich im Linkshänder reflektiert</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Refletiu instintivamente na canhota</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Отразилась в левой руке</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Si è riflessa sulla mano sinistra</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Hidarikiki ni hansha shita</span></p>
      <p begin="00:51.060" end="00:54.860" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L12"><span begin="00:51.060" end="00:51.550">あ</span><span begin="00:51.550" end="00:52.230">あ </span><span begin="00:52.230" end="00:52.700">十</span><span begin="00:52.700" end="00:52.890">は</span><span begin="00:52.890" end="00:53.580">百</span><span begin="00:53.580" end="00:53.680">も</span><span begin="00:53.680" end="00:54.160">承</span><span begin="00:54.160" end="00:54.460">知</span><span begin="00:54.460" end="00:54.690">だ</span><span begin="00:54.690" end="00:54.860">が</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">啊 即便知晓十与百的差距</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">啊 即便知曉十與百的差距</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Ah I am perfectly well aware of that but</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">아아, 열이면 백 다 알고는 있지만</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ah je sais parfaitement ce qu'il en est</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Ah lo sé de sobra pero</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ah mir ist alles wohl bewusst aber</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Ah estou plenamente ciente disso mas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ах я прекрасно осознаю и то и другое но</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ah ne sono perfettamente consapevole</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">A a juu wa hyaku mo shouchi da ga</span></p>
      <p begin="00:55.120" end="00:58.120" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L13"><span begin="00:55.120" end="00:55.390">見</span><span begin="00:55.390" end="00:55.570">抜</span><span begin="00:55.570" end="00:55.830">け</span><span begin="00:55.830" end="00:56.290">よ</span><span begin="00:56.290" end="00:56.340">、</span><span begin="00:56.490" end="00:56.700">蹴</span><span begin="00:56.700" end="00:56.970">飛</span><span begin="00:56.970" end="00:57.210">ば</span><span begin="00:57.210" end="00:57.390">す</span><span begin="00:57.390" end="00:58.120">な</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">也该看透 而非一脚踢开</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">也該看透 而非一腳踢開</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">See through it, don't kick it away</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">꿰뚫어 봐줘, 걷어차지 말고</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Vois clair en moi, ne me rejette pas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Mírame bien no me ignores</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Durchschau es tritt es nicht weg</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Perceba não me chute para longe</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Разгляди это не отталкивай</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ma guardami bene non scacciarmi via</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Minuke yo, ketobasu na</span></p>
      <p begin="00:58.520" end="01:01.900" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L14"><span begin="00:58.520" end="00:58.970">楽</span><span begin="00:58.970" end="00:59.190">し</span><span begin="00:59.190" end="00:59.440">く</span><span begin="00:59.440" end="00:59.680">な</span><span begin="00:59.680" end="00:59.900">い</span><span begin="00:59.900" end="01:00.120">な</span><span begin="01:00.120" end="01:00.170">、</span><span begin="01:00.340" end="01:00.810">正</span><span begin="01:00.810" end="01:00.990">し</span><span begin="01:00.990" end="01:01.200">く</span><span begin="01:01.200" end="01:01.470">な</span><span begin="01:01.470" end="01:01.700">い</span><span begin="01:01.700" end="01:01.900">な</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">这日子真无趣 这般模样也不对</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">這日子真無趣 這般模樣也不對</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">It's not fun, it's not right</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">즐겁지 않아, 바르지 않아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ce n'est pas amusant, ce n'est pas juste</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">No es divertido no es correcto</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Es macht keinen Spaß es ist nicht richtig</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Não é divertido não é correto</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Это не весело это не правильно</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Non è divertente non è giusto</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Tanoshikunai na, tadashikunai na</span></p>
      <p begin="01:02.120" end="01:05.200" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L15"><span begin="01:02.120" end="01:02.590">愛</span><span begin="01:02.590" end="01:03.040">憎</span><span begin="01:03.040" end="01:03.360">な</span><span begin="01:03.360" end="01:03.490">ん</span><span begin="01:03.490" end="01:03.830">て</span><span begin="01:03.830" end="01:04.180">覚</span><span begin="01:04.180" end="01:04.380">え</span><span begin="01:04.380" end="01:04.630">て</span><span begin="01:04.630" end="01:04.870">な</span><span begin="01:04.870" end="01:05.080">い</span><span begin="01:05.080" end="01:05.200">な</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">爱恨之类的情绪 我早已记不清</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">愛恨之類的情緒 我早已記不清</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I don't remember things like love and hate</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">애증 같은 건 기억나지 않아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je ne me souviens plus de l'amour ou de la haine</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">No recuerdo cosas como el amor o el odio</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">An Hass oder Liebe erinnere ich mich nicht</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Não me lembro de coisas como amor e ódio</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я уже и не помню что такое любовь и ненависть</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Non ricordo affatto l'amore e l'odio</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Aizou nante oboetenai na</span></p>
      <p begin="01:05.520" end="01:08.490" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L16"><span begin="01:05.520" end="01:05.970">臓</span><span begin="01:05.970" end="01:06.430">物</span><span begin="01:06.430" end="01:06.660">に</span><span begin="01:06.660" end="01:07.080">響</span><span begin="01:07.080" end="01:07.320">き</span><span begin="01:07.320" end="01:07.780">渡</span><span begin="01:07.780" end="01:08.020">ら</span><span begin="01:08.020" end="01:08.260">な</span><span begin="01:08.260" end="01:08.490">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">过着连脏腑都无法共鸣的生活</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">過著連臟腑都無法共鳴的生活</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Living a life that does not echo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">심장부까지 울려 퍼지지 않는</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Menant une vie qui ne résonne pas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Viviendo una vida que no resuena</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Es hallt nicht in den Eingeweiden wider</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Levando uma vida que não ressoa</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ведя жизнь что не отдаётся эхом</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Conduco una vita che non risuona</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Zoumotsu ni hibiki wataranai</span></p>
      <p begin="01:08.660" end="01:12.720" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L17"><span begin="01:08.660" end="01:09.100">生</span><span begin="01:09.100" end="01:09.570">活</span><span begin="01:09.570" end="01:09.840">を</span><span begin="01:09.840" end="01:10.060">し</span><span begin="01:10.060" end="01:11.060">て </span><span begin="01:11.380" end="01:11.870">紛</span><span begin="01:11.870" end="01:12.720">う</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">试着伪装自己</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">試著偽裝自己</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Through my entrails and being led astray</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">생활을 하며 헷갈려 해</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Dans mes entrailles, je me dissimule</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">En mis entrañas me confundo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Führe ein Leben und täusche mich</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Nas minhas entranhas eu me disfarço</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">В самой глубине нутра я притворяюсь</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Nelle viscere e fingo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Seikatsu o shite magau</span></p>
      <p begin="01:12.940" end="01:16.350" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L18"><span begin="01:12.940" end="01:13.420">楽</span><span begin="01:13.420" end="01:13.620">し</span><span begin="01:13.620" end="01:13.890">く</span><span begin="01:13.890" end="01:14.100">な</span><span begin="01:14.100" end="01:14.300">い</span><span begin="01:14.300" end="01:14.560">な </span><span begin="01:14.800" end="01:15.010">ま</span><span begin="01:15.010" end="01:15.210">る</span><span begin="01:15.210" end="01:15.470">で</span><span begin="01:15.470" end="01:16.100">病</span><span begin="01:16.100" end="01:16.350">だ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">太无趣了 简直像场顽疾</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">太無趣了 簡直像場頑疾</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">It's not fun it's just like a disease</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">즐겁지 않아 마치 병 같아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ce n'est pas amusant, c'est comme une maladie</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">No es divertido es como una enfermedad</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Es macht keinen Spaß fast wie eine Krankheit</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Não é divertido é como uma doença</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Это не весело это словно болезнь</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Non è divertente è proprio come una malattia</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Tanoshikunai na maru de yamaida</span></p>
      <p begin="01:16.560" end="01:19.640" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L19"><span begin="01:16.560" end="01:17.030">夜</span><span begin="01:17.030" end="01:17.230">を</span><span begin="01:17.230" end="01:17.770">貶</span><span begin="01:17.770" end="01:17.930">す</span><span begin="01:17.930" end="01:18.130">の</span><span begin="01:18.130" end="01:18.410">は</span><span begin="01:18.410" end="01:18.710">い</span><span begin="01:18.710" end="01:18.840">つ</span><span begin="01:18.840" end="01:19.040">も</span><span begin="01:19.040" end="01:19.520">善</span><span begin="01:19.520" end="01:19.640">だ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">贬低黑夜的 似乎永远是 “正确”</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">貶低黑夜的 似乎永遠是 「正確」</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">It's always goodness that belittles the night</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">밤을 헐뜯는 건 언제나 선(善)이야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">C'est toujours le bien qui dénigre la nuit</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Siempre es el bien el que desprecia la noche</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Die Nacht zu verleumden ist immer das Gute</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Quem deprecia a noite é sempre o que chamam de bem</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Порицать ночь — это всегда «добро»</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">È sempre il bene a denigrare la notte</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Yoru o kenasu no wa itsumo zen da</span></p>
      <p begin="01:19.960" end="01:25.940" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L20"><span begin="01:19.960" end="01:20.420">誘</span><span begin="01:20.420" end="01:20.870">惑</span><span begin="01:20.870" end="01:21.090">が</span><span begin="01:21.090" end="01:21.550">淘</span><span begin="01:21.550" end="01:21.810">汰</span><span begin="01:21.810" end="01:22.000">す</span><span begin="01:22.000" end="01:22.220">る</span><span begin="01:22.220" end="01:23.130">心</span><span begin="01:23.130" end="01:23.590">の</span><span begin="01:23.590" end="01:23.810">真</span><span begin="01:23.810" end="01:24.030">ん</span><span begin="01:24.030" end="01:24.460">中</span><span begin="01:24.460" end="01:25.940">で</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">在被诱惑筛选过的内心深处</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">在被誘惑篩選過的內心深處</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">In the center of a heart where temptation weeds everything out</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">유혹이 도태시키는 마음 한복판에서</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Au centre de mon cœur éliminé par la tentation</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">En el centro del corazón que la tentación selecciona</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Inmitten des Herzens das die Verführung aussortiert</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">No centro do coração onde a tentação seleciona</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">В самом центре сердца отсеянного искушениями</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Nel mezzo del mio cuore selezionato dalla tentazione</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Yuuwaku ga touta suru kokoro no mannaka de</span></p>
      <p begin="01:26.290" end="01:30.170" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L21"><span begin="01:26.290" end="01:27.200">何</span><span begin="01:27.200" end="01:27.640">を</span><span begin="01:27.640" end="01:27.850">見</span><span begin="01:27.850" end="01:28.330">よ</span><span begin="01:28.330" end="01:30.120">う</span><span begin="01:30.120" end="01:30.170">？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">该看清些什么？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">該看清些什麼？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">What shall I see?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">무엇을 보게 될까?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Que devrais-je regarder ?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">¿Qué debería ver?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Was sollen wir sehen?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">O que devo ver?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">На что мне смотреть?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Cosa dovrei guardare?</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Nani o miyou?</span></p>
      <p begin="01:42.060" end="01:45.460" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L22"><span begin="01:42.060" end="01:42.470">誰</span><span begin="01:42.470" end="01:42.760">か</span><span begin="01:42.760" end="01:43.070">の</span><span begin="01:43.210" end="01:43.670">空</span><span begin="01:43.670" end="01:44.110">白</span><span begin="01:44.110" end="01:44.380">を</span><span begin="01:44.380" end="01:44.560">埋</span><span begin="01:44.560" end="01:44.800">め</span><span begin="01:44.800" end="01:44.990">る</span><span begin="01:44.990" end="01:45.460">度</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">每一次为他人填补空白之时</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">每一次為他人填補空白之時</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Every time I fill in someone's blanks</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">누군가의 공백을 채울 때마다</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Chaque fois que je comble le vide de quelqu'un</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Cada vez que lleno el vacío de alguien</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Jedes Mal wenn ich die Leere von jemandem fülle</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Toda vez que preencho o vazio de alguém</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Каждый раз когда я заполняю чью-то пустоту</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ogni volta che riempio il vuoto di qualcun altro</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Dareka no kuuhaku o umeru tabi</span></p>
      <p begin="01:45.460" end="01:48.540" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L23"><span begin="01:45.460" end="01:45.900">忘</span><span begin="01:45.900" end="01:46.150">れ</span><span begin="01:46.150" end="01:46.370">去</span><span begin="01:46.370" end="01:46.600">れ</span><span begin="01:46.600" end="01:46.810">る</span><span begin="01:46.810" end="01:47.050">も</span><span begin="01:47.050" end="01:47.260">の</span><span begin="01:47.260" end="01:47.440">を</span><span begin="01:47.440" end="01:47.890">教</span><span begin="01:47.890" end="01:48.160">え</span><span begin="01:48.160" end="01:48.540">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">请告诉我 该遗忘些什么</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">請告訴我 該遺忘些什麼</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Tell me the things that can be forgotten</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">잊혀가는 것들을 가르쳐 줘</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Apprends-moi ce qui finit par s'oublier</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Dime qué es lo que se olvida</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Verrate mir was man vergessen kann</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Ensine-me o que deve ser esquecido</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Расскажи мне о том что будет забыто</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Dimmi le cose che andrebbero dimenticate</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Wasure sareru mono o oshiete</span></p>
      <p begin="01:49.260" end="01:52.660" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L24"><span begin="01:49.260" end="01:49.730">言</span><span begin="01:49.730" end="01:49.970">葉</span><span begin="01:49.970" end="01:50.270">に</span><span begin="01:50.400" end="01:50.870">優</span><span begin="01:50.870" end="01:51.290">劣</span><span begin="01:51.290" end="01:51.600">を</span><span begin="01:51.600" end="01:51.730">つ</span><span begin="01:51.730" end="01:52.000">け</span><span begin="01:52.000" end="01:52.210">る</span><span begin="01:52.210" end="01:52.660">度</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">每一次给语言分出优劣之时</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">每一次給語言分出優劣之時</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Every time I rank words as superior or inferior</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">말에 우열을 가릴 때마다</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Chaque fois que l'on donne une hiérarchie aux mots</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Cada vez que doy prioridad a las palabras</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Jedes Mal wenn man Worten Ränge verleiht</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Toda vez que dou prioridade às palavras</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Каждый раз когда я разделяю слова на лучшие и худшие</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ogni volta che do una priorità alle parole</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kotoba ni yuuretsu o tsukeru tabi</span></p>
      <p begin="01:52.660" end="01:55.740" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L25"><span begin="01:52.660" end="01:53.120">薄</span><span begin="01:53.120" end="01:53.350">れ</span><span begin="01:53.350" end="01:53.590">て</span><span begin="01:53.590" end="01:53.800">い</span><span begin="01:53.800" end="01:54.010">く</span><span begin="01:54.010" end="01:54.270">価</span><span begin="01:54.270" end="01:54.470">値</span><span begin="01:54.470" end="01:54.660">を</span><span begin="01:54.660" end="01:55.150">教</span><span begin="01:55.150" end="01:55.380">え</span><span begin="01:55.380" end="01:55.740">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">请告诉我 正消散的价值是什么</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">請告訴我 正消散的價值是什麼</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Tell me the value that keeps fading away</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">흐려지는 가치를 가르쳐 줘</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Apprends-moi quelle valeur s'efface</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Dime cuál es el valor que se desvanece</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Verrate mir den Wert der verblasst</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Ensine-me o valor que está se dissipando</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Расскажи мне о ценности что постепенно исчезает</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Dimmi il valore che svanisce</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Usurete iku kachi o oshiete</span></p>
      <p begin="01:56.040" end="01:59.880" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L26"><span begin="01:56.040" end="01:56.500">悪</span><span begin="01:56.500" end="01:56.970">戯</span><span begin="01:56.970" end="01:57.150">に</span><span begin="01:57.150" end="01:57.660">贅</span><span begin="01:57.660" end="01:57.840">を</span><span begin="01:57.840" end="01:58.080">尽</span><span begin="01:58.080" end="01:58.370">く</span><span begin="01:58.370" end="01:58.540">す</span><span begin="01:58.540" end="01:58.750">だ</span><span begin="01:58.750" end="01:59.210">け</span><span begin="01:59.210" end="01:59.400">の</span><span begin="01:59.400" end="01:59.880">性</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">天性中 只懂肆意挥霍的任性</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">天性中 只懂肆意揮霍的任性</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">A nature that only indulges in luxury mischievously</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">장난스럽게 사치를 부릴 뿐인 천성</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Cette nature de ne faire que gaspiller le luxe par caprice</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Esa naturaleza de solo gastar lujos en vano</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Das Wesen das nur mutwillig im Luxus schwelgt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">A natureza de apenas esbanjar o luxo por travessura</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Сущность лишь в том чтобы тратить всё на пустую роскошь</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">La natura di sprecare lussuria per capriccio</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Itazura ni zei o tsukusu dake no saga</span></p>
      <p begin="02:00.120" end="02:03.020" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L27"><span begin="02:00.120" end="02:00.350">生</span><span begin="02:00.350" end="02:00.570">ま</span><span begin="02:00.570" end="02:00.730">れ</span><span begin="02:00.730" end="02:01.080">つ</span><span begin="02:01.080" end="02:01.260">き</span><span begin="02:01.260" end="02:01.430">に</span><span begin="02:01.430" end="02:01.870">甘</span><span begin="02:01.870" end="02:02.110">受</span><span begin="02:02.110" end="02:02.370">し</span><span begin="02:02.370" end="02:03.020">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">生来便只能默默承受</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">生來便只能默默承受</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Accepted it by birth</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">태어날 때부터 받아들여 버렸어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je l'ai acceptée dès ma naissance</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">La acepté desde mi nacimiento</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Habe ich von Geburt an hingenommen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Aceitei isso por nascimento</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я смирилась с этим от самого рождения</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">L'ho accettata fin dalla nascita</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Umaretsuki ni kanju shita</span></p>
      <p begin="02:03.250" end="02:07.050" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L28"><span begin="02:03.250" end="02:03.910">あ</span><span begin="02:03.910" end="02:04.380">あ </span><span begin="02:04.380" end="02:04.870">刑</span><span begin="02:04.870" end="02:05.070">も</span><span begin="02:05.070" end="02:05.770">虐</span><span begin="02:05.770" end="02:06.010">も</span><span begin="02:06.010" end="02:06.430">演</span><span begin="02:06.430" end="02:06.670">技</span><span begin="02:06.670" end="02:06.890">な</span><span begin="02:06.890" end="02:07.050">ら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">啊 若惩罚与虐待都是伪装</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">啊 若懲罰與虐待都是偽裝</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Ah if both punishment and cruelty are just acting</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">아아, 형벌도 학대도 연기라면</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ah si le châtiment et la cruauté ne sont que comédie</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Ah si el castigo y la tortura son actuación</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ah wenn Strafe und Qual nur Schauspiel sind</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Ah se a punição e a crueldade forem encenações</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ах если наказание и истязание лишь игра</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ah se la pena e il tormento sono solo una recita</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">A a kei mo gyaku mo engi nara</span></p>
      <p begin="02:07.270" end="02:10.470" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L29"><span begin="02:07.270" end="02:07.570">そ</span><span begin="02:07.570" end="02:07.760">の</span><span begin="02:07.760" end="02:08.000">眼</span><span begin="02:08.000" end="02:08.480">を</span><span begin="02:08.480" end="02:08.540">、</span><span begin="02:08.700" end="02:08.920">誤</span><span begin="02:08.920" end="02:09.110">魔</span><span begin="02:09.110" end="02:09.400">化</span><span begin="02:09.400" end="02:09.600">す</span><span begin="02:09.600" end="02:10.470">な</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">就别再蒙蔽那双眼睛</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">就別再蒙蔽那雙眼睛</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Then those eyes, do not deceive them</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그 눈을 속이지 마</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">N'abuse pas de tes propres yeux</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">No engañes a esos ojos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Dann täusche diese Augen nicht</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Não engane esses olhos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">То не обманывай эти глаза</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Non ingannare quegli occhi</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sono me o, gomakasu na</span></p>
      <p begin="02:25.160" end="02:27.620" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L30"><span begin="02:25.160" end="02:25.390">名</span><span begin="02:25.390" end="02:25.830">前</span><span begin="02:25.830" end="02:26.060">も</span><span begin="02:26.060" end="02:26.540">無</span><span begin="02:26.540" end="02:26.700">い</span><span begin="02:26.700" end="02:27.620">位</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">连名字都没有的</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">連名字都沒有的</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">To the point of being nameless</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">이름조차 없을 만큼</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Au point de ne plus avoir de nom</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Hasta el punto de no tener nombre</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">So sehr dass es nicht einmal einen Namen hat</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">A ponto de nem ter nome</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">К чувствам столь хрупким тёмным и ничтожным</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Al punto da non avere nemmeno un nome</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Namae mo nai kurai</span></p>
      <p begin="02:27.640" end="02:31.740" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L31"><span begin="02:27.640" end="02:28.320">脆</span><span begin="02:28.320" end="02:28.500">い</span><span begin="02:28.500" end="02:29.230">暗</span><span begin="02:29.230" end="02:29.440">い</span><span begin="02:29.440" end="02:29.690">些</span><span begin="02:29.690" end="02:30.130">細</span><span begin="02:30.130" end="02:30.350">な</span><span begin="02:30.350" end="02:30.780">感</span><span begin="02:30.780" end="02:31.260">情</span><span begin="02:31.260" end="02:31.740">に</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">脆弱、灰暗又渺小的情绪</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">脆弱、灰暗又渺小的情緒</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Starting to notice the fragile dark</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">취약하고 어둡고 사소한 감정에</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">En ces sentiments fragiles, sombres et infimes</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">En estas emociones frágiles oscuras y pequeñas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">In zerbrechlichen dunklen trivialen Gefühlen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Nas emoções frágeis sombrias e triviais</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Что у них нет даже названия</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">In queste fragili oscure e piccole emozioni</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Moroi kurai sasai na kanjou ni</span></p>
      <p begin="02:31.900" end="02:33.580" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L32"><span begin="02:31.900" end="02:32.130">気</span><span begin="02:32.130" end="02:32.380">づ</span><span begin="02:32.380" end="02:32.600">い</span><span begin="02:32.600" end="02:32.840">て</span><span begin="02:32.840" end="02:33.050">い</span><span begin="02:33.050" end="02:33.580">く</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">正一点点被察觉</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">正一點點被察覺</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">And trivial emotions</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">어느덧 깨닫게 돼</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je commence à m'éveiller</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Me voy dando cuenta</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Werde ich mir ihrer bewusst</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Vou percebendo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я начинаю привыкать</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Inizio ad accorgermi</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kizuite iku</span></p>
      <p begin="02:33.900" end="02:39.060" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L33"><span begin="02:33.900" end="02:34.420">思</span><span begin="02:34.420" end="02:34.810">い</span><span begin="02:34.810" end="02:35.070">出</span><span begin="02:35.070" end="02:35.330">す</span><span begin="02:35.330" end="02:35.740">度</span><span begin="02:35.740" end="02:36.460">に </span><span begin="02:36.630" end="02:37.290">怯</span><span begin="02:37.290" end="02:37.550">え</span><span begin="02:37.550" end="02:37.940">て</span><span begin="02:37.940" end="02:38.250">し</span><span begin="02:38.250" end="02:38.490">ま</span><span begin="02:38.490" end="02:39.060">う</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">每一次回想 都会忍不住颤抖</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">每一次回想 都會忍不住顫抖</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Every time I remember I get frightened</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">떠올릴 때마다 겁이 나버려</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Chaque fois que je m'en souviens, je finis par trembler</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Cada vez que lo recuerdo me asusto</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Jedes Mal wenn ich mich erinnere erzittere ich</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Toda vez que me lembro acabo tremendo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Каждый раз вспоминая я содрогаюсь от страха</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ogni volta che ricordo inizio a tremare</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Omoidasu tabi ni obiete shimau</span></p>
      <p begin="02:39.270" end="02:43.560" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L34"><span begin="02:39.270" end="02:39.610">そ</span><span begin="02:39.610" end="02:39.810">れ</span><span begin="02:39.810" end="02:40.050">で</span><span begin="02:40.050" end="02:40.280">も</span><span begin="02:40.280" end="02:40.500">ま</span><span begin="02:40.500" end="02:41.100">だ </span><span begin="02:41.100" end="02:41.860">眩</span><span begin="02:41.860" end="02:42.030">む</span><span begin="02:42.030" end="02:42.290">揺</span><span begin="02:42.290" end="02:42.770">ら</span><span begin="02:42.770" end="02:42.950">ぐ</span><span begin="02:42.950" end="02:43.220">ま</span><span begin="02:43.220" end="02:43.560">ま</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">即便如此 依旧在眩晕与摇晃中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">即便如此 依舊在眩暈與搖晃中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Even so while still dizzy and swaying</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그럼에도 여전히 눈이 멀고 흔들리는 채로</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Pourtant, tout en étant encore éblouie et chancelante</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Aun así sigo mareada y tambaleante</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Trotzdem noch immer schwindelig und schwankend</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Mesmo assim ainda tonta e instável</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Но всё же до сих пор в этом головокружении и дрожи</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Eppure ancora mentre tutto vacilla e barcolla</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sore demo mada kuramu yuragu mama</span></p>
      <p begin="02:43.890" end="02:47.180" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L35"><span begin="02:43.890" end="02:44.100">鳴</span><span begin="02:44.100" end="02:44.710">り</span><span begin="02:44.710" end="02:45.250">響</span><span begin="02:45.250" end="02:45.470">い</span><span begin="02:45.470" end="02:45.700">て</span><span begin="02:45.700" end="02:45.910">い</span><span begin="02:45.910" end="02:47.180">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">任由声响回荡</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">任由聲響回盪</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">It's ringing out</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">울려 퍼지고 있어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Cela continue de résonner</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Resuenan sin parar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Hallt es wider</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Continua ecoando</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Продолжает звучать эхо</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sta risuonando</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Narihibiite iru</span></p>
      <p begin="02:47.610" end="02:53.720" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L36"><span begin="02:47.610" end="02:48.020">灰</span><span begin="02:48.020" end="02:48.380">色</span><span begin="02:48.380" end="02:48.810">見</span><span begin="02:48.810" end="02:49.070">出</span><span begin="02:49.070" end="02:49.330">す</span><span begin="02:49.330" end="02:49.730">体</span><span begin="02:49.730" end="02:50.170">温</span><span begin="02:50.170" end="02:50.660">で </span><span begin="02:50.660" end="02:51.090">今</span><span begin="02:51.090" end="02:52.160">が</span><span begin="02:52.400" end="02:52.640">更</span><span begin="02:52.640" end="02:52.910">け</span><span begin="02:52.910" end="02:53.720">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">用寻得灰色的体温 迎接此刻的深夜</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">用尋得灰色的體溫 迎接此刻的深夜</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">With the body temperature finding grey the night deepens</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">회색빛을 찾아낸 체온으로 지금 이 밤이 깊어져</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Avec une température trouvant sa place dans le gris, l'instant s'achève</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Con una temperatura que halla el gris el ahora se oscurece</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Mit der Körpertemperatur die das Grau findet vergeht das Jetzt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Com a temperatura corporal que encontra o cinza a noite se aprofunda</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">С температурой в которой я нашла серость ночь сгущается</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">La notte si fa fonda con una temperatura che trova il grigio</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Haiiro midasu taion de ima ga fukeru</span></p>
      <p begin="02:54.000" end="02:57.380" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L37"><span begin="02:54.000" end="02:54.440">楽</span><span begin="02:54.440" end="02:54.670">し</span><span begin="02:54.670" end="02:54.910">く</span><span begin="02:54.910" end="02:55.160">な</span><span begin="02:55.160" end="02:55.390">い</span><span begin="02:55.390" end="02:55.560">な</span><span begin="02:55.560" end="02:55.610">、</span><span begin="02:55.780" end="02:56.230">正</span><span begin="02:56.230" end="02:56.470">し</span><span begin="02:56.470" end="02:56.690">く</span><span begin="02:56.690" end="02:56.940">な</span><span begin="02:56.940" end="02:57.170">い</span><span begin="02:57.170" end="02:57.380">な</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">这日子真无趣 这般模样也不对</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">這日子真無趣 這般模樣也不對</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">It's not fun, it's not right</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">즐겁지 않아, 바르지 않아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ce n'est pas amusant, ce n'est pas juste</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">No es divertido no es correcto</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Es macht keinen Spaß es ist nicht richtig</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Não é divertido não é correto</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Это не весело это не правильно</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Non è divertente non è giusto</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Tanoshikunai na, tadashikunai na</span></p>
      <p begin="02:57.610" end="03:00.910" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L38"><span begin="02:57.610" end="02:58.070">愛</span><span begin="02:58.070" end="02:58.480">憎</span><span begin="02:58.480" end="02:58.730">な</span><span begin="02:58.730" end="02:58.970">ん</span><span begin="02:58.970" end="02:59.200">て</span><span begin="02:59.200" end="02:59.690">覚</span><span begin="02:59.690" end="02:59.880">え</span><span begin="02:59.880" end="03:00.130">て</span><span begin="03:00.130" end="03:00.350">な</span><span begin="03:00.350" end="03:00.570">い</span><span begin="03:00.570" end="03:00.910">な</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">爱恨之类的情绪 我早已记不清</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">愛恨之類的情緒 我早已記不清</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I don't remember things like love and hate</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">애증 같은 건 기억나지 않아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je ne me souviens plus de l'amour ou de la haine</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">No recuerdo cosas como el amor o el odio</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">An Hass oder Liebe erinnere ich mich nicht</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Não me lembro de coisas como amor e ódio</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я уже и не помню что такое любовь и ненависть</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Non ricordo affatto l'amore e l'odio</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Aizou nante oboetenai na</span></p>
      <p begin="03:01.020" end="03:03.990" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L39"><span begin="03:01.020" end="03:01.460">臓</span><span begin="03:01.460" end="03:01.910">物</span><span begin="03:01.910" end="03:02.060">に</span><span begin="03:02.060" end="03:02.590">響</span><span begin="03:02.590" end="03:02.820">き</span><span begin="03:02.820" end="03:03.280">渡</span><span begin="03:03.280" end="03:03.510">ら</span><span begin="03:03.510" end="03:03.750">な</span><span begin="03:03.750" end="03:03.990">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">过着连脏腑都无法共鸣的生活</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">過著連臟腑都無法共鳴的生活</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Living a life that does not echo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">심장부까지 울려 퍼지지 않는</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Menant une vie qui ne résonne pas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Viviendo una vida que no resuena</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Es hallt nicht in den Eingeweiden wider</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Levando uma vida que não ressoa</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ведя жизнь что не отдаётся эхом</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Conduco una vita che non risuona</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Zoumotsu ni hibiki wataranai</span></p>
      <p begin="03:04.120" end="03:08.180" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L40"><span begin="03:04.120" end="03:04.560">生</span><span begin="03:04.560" end="03:05.100">活</span><span begin="03:05.100" end="03:05.290">を</span><span begin="03:05.290" end="03:05.510">し</span><span begin="03:05.510" end="03:06.510">て </span><span begin="03:06.820" end="03:07.350">紛</span><span begin="03:07.350" end="03:08.180">う</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">试着伪装自己</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">試著偽裝自己</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Through my entrails and being led astray</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">생활을 하며 헷갈려 해</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Dans mes entrailles, je me dissimule</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">En mis entrañas me confundo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Führe ein Leben und täusche mich</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Nas minhas entranhas eu me disfarço</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">В самой глубине нутра я притворяюсь</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Nelle viscere e fingo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Seikatsu o shite magau</span></p>
      <p begin="03:08.450" end="03:11.830" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L41"><span begin="03:08.450" end="03:08.700">あ</span><span begin="03:08.700" end="03:08.910">な</span><span begin="03:08.910" end="03:09.140">た</span><span begin="03:09.140" end="03:09.290">の</span><span begin="03:09.290" end="03:09.550">所</span><span begin="03:09.550" end="03:09.820">為</span><span begin="03:09.820" end="03:10.050">だ</span><span begin="03:10.050" end="03:10.100">、</span><span begin="03:10.280" end="03:10.490">ま</span><span begin="03:10.490" end="03:10.710">る</span><span begin="03:10.710" end="03:10.960">で</span><span begin="03:10.960" end="03:11.620">病</span><span begin="03:11.620" end="03:11.830">だ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">全是你的缘故 简直像场顽疾</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">全是你的緣故 簡直像場頑疾</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">It's your fault, it's just like a disease</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">당신 때문이야, 마치 병 같아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">C'est de ta faute, c'est comme une maladie</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Es por tu culpa es como una enfermedad</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Es ist deine Schuld fast wie eine Krankheit</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">A culpa é sua é como uma doença</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Это всё из-за тебя это словно болезнь</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">È colpa tua è proprio come una malattia</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Anata no sei da, maru de yamaida</span></p>
      <p begin="03:12.060" end="03:15.180" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L42"><span begin="03:12.060" end="03:12.300">エ</span><span begin="03:12.300" end="03:12.530">ゴ</span><span begin="03:12.530" end="03:12.760">で</span><span begin="03:12.760" end="03:12.970">満</span><span begin="03:12.970" end="03:13.230">た</span><span begin="03:13.230" end="03:13.430">し</span><span begin="03:13.430" end="03:13.630">た</span><span begin="03:13.630" end="03:13.870">だ</span><span begin="03:13.870" end="03:14.100">け</span><span begin="03:14.100" end="03:14.320">の</span><span begin="03:14.320" end="03:14.570">偽</span><span begin="03:14.570" end="03:15.020">善</span><span begin="03:15.020" end="03:15.180">だ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">不过是用自私填满的伪善</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">不過是用自私填滿的偽善</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">It's just hypocrisy filled with only ego</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">이기심으로 채웠을 뿐인 위선이야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ce n'est qu'une hypocrisie remplie d'ego</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Es solo hipocresía llena de ego</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Es ist Heuchelei die nur mit Ego gefüllt ist</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">É apenas hipocrisia preenchida por ego</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Это лишь прикрытая эгоизмом притворная добродетель</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">È solo ipocrisia riempita di ego</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ego de mitashita dake no gizenda</span></p>
      <p begin="03:15.450" end="03:21.430" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L43"><span begin="03:15.450" end="03:15.910">欲</span><span begin="03:15.910" end="03:16.350">望</span><span begin="03:16.350" end="03:16.460">に</span><span begin="03:16.460" end="03:17.050">終</span><span begin="03:17.050" end="03:17.240">始</span><span begin="03:17.240" end="03:17.490">す</span><span begin="03:17.490" end="03:17.710">る</span><span begin="03:17.710" end="03:18.630">心</span><span begin="03:18.630" end="03:19.070">の</span><span begin="03:19.070" end="03:19.340">真</span><span begin="03:19.340" end="03:19.520">ん</span><span begin="03:19.520" end="03:19.990">中</span><span begin="03:19.990" end="03:21.430">に</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">在始终被欲望支配的内心深处</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">在始終被慾望支配的內心深處</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">In the center of a heart consisting only of desire</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">욕망으로 점철된 마음 한가운데서</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Au centre de ce cœur dominé par le désir</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">En el centro del corazón que empieza y termina en el deseo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Mitten im Herzen das in Verlangen endet</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">No centro do coração que começa e termina no desejo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">В самом центре сердца подвластного желаниям</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Nel mezzo del mio cuore dominato dal desiderio</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Yokubou ni shuushi suru kokoro no mannaka ni</span></p>
      <p begin="03:21.720" end="03:25.570" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L44"><span begin="03:21.720" end="03:22.680">夜</span><span begin="03:22.680" end="03:23.120">を</span><span begin="03:23.120" end="03:23.330">見</span><span begin="03:23.330" end="03:24.720">よ</span><span begin="03:24.720" end="03:25.570">う</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">正视这黑夜吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">正視這黑夜吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Let's look at the night</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">밤을 직시하자</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Regardons la nuit</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Miremos la noche</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Lass uns in die Nacht blicken</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Vamos encarar a noite</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я буду смотреть в ночь</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Guardiamo la notte</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Yoru o miyou</span></p>
      <p begin="03:37.520" end="03:40.820" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L45"><span begin="03:37.520" end="03:37.780">あ</span><span begin="03:37.780" end="03:38.000">な</span><span begin="03:38.000" end="03:38.230">た</span><span begin="03:38.230" end="03:38.540">が</span><span begin="03:38.670" end="03:39.140">行</span><span begin="03:39.140" end="03:39.610">先</span><span begin="03:39.610" end="03:39.860">を</span><span begin="03:39.860" end="03:40.300">憂</span><span begin="03:40.300" end="03:40.490">う</span><span begin="03:40.490" end="03:40.820">度</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">你每一次担忧前路之时</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">你每一次擔憂前路之時</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Every time you grieve over your destination</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">당신이 행방을 걱정할 때마다</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Chaque fois que tu t'inquiètes de ta destination</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Cada vez que te angustias por el destino</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Jedes Mal wenn du dich um das Ziel sorgst</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Toda vez que você se angustia com o destino</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Каждый раз когда ты тревожишься о пути</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ogni volta che ti preoccupi della destinazione</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Anata ga ikisaki o ureu tabi</span></p>
      <p begin="03:40.870" end="03:43.840" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L46"><span begin="03:40.870" end="03:41.350">悲</span><span begin="03:41.350" end="03:41.580">し</span><span begin="03:41.580" end="03:41.850">く</span><span begin="03:41.850" end="03:42.070">な</span><span begin="03:42.070" end="03:42.280">る</span><span begin="03:42.280" end="03:42.510">意</span><span begin="03:42.510" end="03:42.760">味</span><span begin="03:42.760" end="03:42.900">を</span><span begin="03:42.900" end="03:43.400">教</span><span begin="03:43.400" end="03:43.600">え</span><span begin="03:43.600" end="03:43.840">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">请告诉我 变得悲伤的意义</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">請告訴我 變得悲傷的意義</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Tell me the meaning of becoming sad</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">슬퍼지는 의미를 가르쳐 줘</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Apprends-moi le sens de devenir triste</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Dime el significado de entristecerse</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Verrate mir den Sinn traurig zu werden</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Ensine-me o significado de me tornar triste</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Расскажи мне в чём смысл того что становится грустно</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Dimmi il significato di diventare tristi</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kanashiku naru imi o oshiete</span></p>
      <p begin="03:44.810" end="03:48.050" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L47"><span begin="03:44.810" end="03:45.430">私</span><span begin="03:45.430" end="03:45.650">が</span><span begin="03:45.840" end="03:46.290">幸</span><span begin="03:46.290" end="03:46.820">福</span><span begin="03:46.820" end="03:47.020">に</span><span begin="03:47.020" end="03:47.250">触</span><span begin="03:47.250" end="03:47.500">れ</span><span begin="03:47.500" end="03:47.690">る</span><span begin="03:47.690" end="03:48.050">度</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我每一次触碰幸福之时</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我每一次觸碰幸福之時</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Every time I touch happiness</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">내가 행복을 만질 때마다</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Chaque fois que je touche au bonheur</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Cada vez que toco la felicidad</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Jedes Mal wenn ich das Glück berühre</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Toda vez que eu toco na felicidade</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Каждый раз когда я касаюсь счастья</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ogni volta che io tocco la felicità</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Watashi ga koufuku ni fureru tabi</span></p>
      <p begin="03:48.090" end="03:51.060" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L48"><span begin="03:48.090" end="03:48.620">騒</span><span begin="03:48.620" end="03:48.830">め</span><span begin="03:48.830" end="03:49.040">き</span><span begin="03:49.040" end="03:49.340">出</span><span begin="03:49.340" end="03:49.490">す</span><span begin="03:49.490" end="03:49.950">声</span><span begin="03:49.950" end="03:50.130">に</span><span begin="03:50.130" end="03:50.380">気</span><span begin="03:50.380" end="03:50.630">づ</span><span begin="03:50.630" end="03:50.860">い</span><span begin="03:50.860" end="03:51.060">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">请留意 那些骤然喧闹的声音</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">請留意 那些驟然喧鬧的聲音</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Notice the voices starting to stir</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">술렁이기 시작하는 목소리를 알아차려 줘</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Remarque ces voix qui commencent à s'agiter</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Date cuenta de las voces que empiezan a agitarse</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Bemerke die Stimmen die aufruhen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Perceba as vozes que começam a se agitar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Заметь этот голос что начинает шуметь</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Accorgiti delle voci che iniziano a sussurrare</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Zawamekidasu koe ni kizuite</span></p>
      <p begin="03:51.550" end="03:52.690" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L49"><span begin="03:51.550" end="03:51.770">い</span><span begin="03:51.770" end="03:51.980">い</span><span begin="03:51.980" end="03:52.220">で</span><span begin="03:52.220" end="03:52.420">す</span><span begin="03:52.420" end="03:52.640">か</span><span begin="03:52.640" end="03:52.690">？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">可以吗？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">可以嗎？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Is it alright?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">괜찮을까?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Est-ce permis ?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">¿Te parece bien?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ist es in Ordnung?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Tudo bem?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Можно ли?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Va bene?</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ii desu ka?</span></p>
    </div>
  </body>
</tt>
